snippet.title: Race the Sun - Sunrise DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.gog.com/game/sunrise

Enjoy an all-new way to experience Race The Sun with this endless, zen-like game mode.

No leaderboards, no setting sun - just endless, rewarding flight.
